Text: Interviews with Fleetwood Mac members and live music clips from 1976 and 1989. From Dutch television back then (without Dutch subtitling). Resize to 16:9 yourself. Good webstream quality. I cannot cut .asf, so you have Cream documentary and part Little Feat at Rockpalast 1977 as a bonus. I am not sure whether music clips in Fleetwood stuff are really difficult to find on the net, but the interviews are.
Anyone has a nice audio recording from Fleetwood Mac in Antwerp (Antwerpen) on the 14th of October 2009? Please, please upload that goodie!
